k.\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2476, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2410}, {\"ngram\": \"justice\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2463}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"See you in court.\\\"\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"court\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The case is not dissimilar to one Fox lost earlier this year against British drag artist Crystal.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2533, \"end\": 2536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9999388633770183, \"rank\": 6.070066144083795e-05, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 2568, \"end\": 2575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9944667444750818, \"rank\": 0.004588718060141509, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The case\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 46-year-old was ordered to pay \\u00a390,000 in damages to Crystal and former Stonewall trustee Simon Blake after referring to them as \\\"paedophiles\\\" in an exchange on X/Twitter.\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2673, \"end\": 2682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stonewall_riots\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.757765650065643e-30, \"text\": \"Stonewall\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stonewall_riots\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stonewall_riots\"}, {\"begin\": 2697, \"end\": 2702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Blake\", \"score\": 0.9275045298053864, \"rank\": 0.078161850